data.description: This lovely 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home is perfect for new owners seeking space and convenience. It boasts four bedrooms, a loft, and a fully finished basement complete with a private movie theater. The modern kitchen features stainless steel appliances, and there's ample parking with a two-car garage and two additional spaces. The primary bedroom includes a spacious walk-in closet and ensuite bathroom. The versatile loft can be used as a workspace or play area. Outside, the huge gated backyard is ideal for relaxing summer days and hosting family gatherings. Move in Ready.  Pre-approved buyer only.
